sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Nasabah
    participant APP as Mobile App
    participant PAY as Servicing
    participant PGW as Payment Gateway
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>APP: Bayar (jumlah < tagihan)
    APP->>PAY: POST /payments (Idempotency-Key)
    PAY->>PGW: proses pembayaran
    PGW-->>PAY: SUCCESS
    PAY->>PAY: alokasi waterfall (denda→bunga→pokok) (BR-09)
    PAY->>DB: update schedule = PARTIALLY_PAID
    PAY->>DB: outstanding_balance -= pokok terbayar
    PAY->>DB: insert payment (rincian alokasi) + transaction
    PAY-->>APP: 200 OK (sisa tagihan)
